  "texts": [
    "However, at the same time the know-how and agility of the industry should be included in the formulation of frameworks so that the regulatory endeavors remain both timely and effective.",
    "This means that the potentially best solution would take advantage of both institutional characteristics.",
    "The following chapter provides an example of how such a solution could look like.",
    "Proposing an institutional network Dynamic laws in AI regulationCombining what we have discussed so far, the present chapter intends to introduce a novel solution, which would be a regulatory body that is connected to international organizations and hosts hearings for corporations.",
    "The idea revolves around establishing a governmental body with the authority to create and implement transitory regulations."
